{"tid":731263,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"高達 GUNDAM 開拍真人版電影 景甜準備扮馬茜．傳奇影業全力支援","createTime":"2018-07-06T05:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T09:59:03.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d226848aab9727045237f907752624281362bb","tid":731263,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"《機動戰士高達 電影版》Mobile Suit Gundam 的CG Live Action Movie正式開拍！將由景甜御用、傳奇影業LEGENDARY Pictures 負責製作，上映日期未定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1616176/org/38e11fea915e31bf1508cfb4ed510230.jpg/LIgs-qQ_722vYs7EoRaNppyiPQQvwW_piJgs8IiYLPA?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1616176%2Forg%2F38e11fea915e31bf1508cfb4ed510230.jpg%2FLIgs-qQ_722vYs7EoRaNppyiPQQvwW_piJgs8IiYLPA%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=e5ddc14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《機動戰士高達》Mobile Suit Gundam 已有40多年歷史，7月6日，全球鋼彈迷應該高興，因為CG Live Action Movie已經正式計畫開拍了。<br />\n<br />\n都是《挑戰者一號》的錯，三分鐘 CG高達 演出，令全球GUMDA FANS重燃「荷里活版高達」的希望！甚至有傳Dream works已經開始拍攝、史匹堡監製等網上吹水新聞。現在，萬達集團旗下的傳奇影業LEGENDARY Pictures 正式走出來，宣布與BANDAI NAMCO、Sunrise合拍《機動戰士高達 電影版》Mobile Suit Gundam 的CG Live Action Movie！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1616160/org/34bf80b99113e776315efbc23b480223.jpg/kIM69nJjUjniCK-giLvzPA9ZJd9_d9JiN-4eEDfuHhA?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1616160%2Forg%2F34bf80b99113e776315efbc23b480223.jpg%2FkIM69nJjUjniCK-giLvzPA9ZJd9_d9JiN-4eEDfuHhA%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=66dbeb91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首張宣傳海報，地球上出現好大個Ｇ點，代表世人都為景甜入主高達而興奮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1616157/org/d9b9e071cafa8edc6c32e104009f78bd.jpg/MFHXipWo9XbTyrXtoNlu4QDjgr0QNdIrBwfgVQcH4FU?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1616157%2Forg%2Fd9b9e071cafa8edc6c32e104009f78bd.jpg%2FMFHXipWo9XbTyrXtoNlu4QDjgr0QNdIrBwfgVQcH4FU%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=2d026e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7月4日，傳奇影業跟SUNRISE、BANDAI NAMCO在LA舉行的ANIME EXPO內宣布電影計畫。<br />\n<br />\n最想睇景甜扮扮馬茜還是娜娜？<br />\nLEGENDARY Pictures 拍攝的《長城》、《金剛 骷髏島》、《悍戰太平洋2：起義時空》，無獨有偶都有國際級電影女星景甜演出，相信今次《高達》真人版同樣會有她的份兒，FANS真的要好好期待。大家最想看她扮馬茜還是娜娜呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/遊戲動漫/207364/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%8B%95%E6%BC%AB%2F207364%2F&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2aaaa510\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/遊戲動漫/207364/</a>"},{"pid":"92b8df21b4ea4c446fb941b9e826c7d69b998f76","tid":731263,"uid":93062,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"想當年嘅鬼佬龍珠,我就唔知睇咗咩<br />\n<br />\n今日仲同我講高達真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb35b6a78e307f5964ba65f72ab28ccfd29d7e06","tid":731263,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"景甜世界級"},{"pid":"4d71ae767269adebdb1f4d9f4042896facb7e798","tid":731263,"uid":60977,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"富野睇完等入棺材"},{"pid":"5ec1ef479101ee2953a75e8eb925397f6bf124c9","tid":731263,"uid":70033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"g saviour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0d04d42d8b5a3c24c819804b144dd058158fd7","tid":731263,"uid":11310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"景甜個後台好似好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n套套中國上映荷李活電影都有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83995856a180aa71a86db5bf6f410267d2985c20","tid":731263,"uid":81059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"我愈來愈懷疑景甜其實姓 習"},{"pid":"3ec32a77c601e1292f2e1532daeadfa5a1871603","tid":731263,"uid":29270,"like":0,"d